content: I've been doing some of these already, like posting regularly and using a consistent aesthetic. It's great to know I'm on the right track. Speaking of which, I'm curious to know if there's a way to see which posts are performing well and which ones aren't. Do you know if Instagram Insights can help me with that? And by the way, I've got 1250 followers on Instagram now, so it'd be great to get some insights on how to optimize my content for them.
